registry/assessments/nsk1-g2d.json:71:      "correctness_thesis": "Strengthens the exhaustion doc section 4a narrowing with a mechanism and a scale extension: the viable delivery region for checked kernel content excludes the append-as-text channel not just at tiny hosts (disruption) but at capable hosts (substitution). Topologies where the ENGINE consumes kernel content (select/verify/retry, f2b-shaped) remain the only measured-positive delivery class; the internal residual-stream class remains unmeasured.",
registry/assessments/nsk1-g2d.json:77:      {"claim": "2-hop entity-form composition capability exists in the SmolLM2-Instruct family without weight changes (1.7B zero-shot 0.76; 360M few-shot 0.77)", "from": "EXTRAPOLATION (exhaustion doc proposed-ASM-C, unregistered)", "to": "MEASURED-exploratory", "scope": "CLUTRR entity form, this 100-item slice, greedy fp32 chat-template max_new_tokens=16; NOT the relation form, NOT the custom surface, NOT verdict-grade", "backing": "g2d_summary.json sha256 93a6e951... cells R3/clutrr/2 and R2/clutrr/2"},
