registry/assessments/oracle-coverage.json:42:        "Membership census, not usability: a covered token is one whose lemma is reachable in the kernel vocabulary — it says nothing about whether the covering entry's explication is sound (g2/g3 territory, unmeasured) or useful (Tier-1 territory, unmeasured). Downstream, the compression-census assessment measured that proposition-level ENGAGEMENT on this same corpus/instance is ~0.6% — two orders below token-mass coverage — so 0.3542 must never be read as 'fraction of corpus the kernel can do something with'.",
registry/assessments/oracle-coverage.json:50:      "means_for_correctness_thesis": "This is the first MEASURED existence proof of the programme's own Law-3 engine seat: a native (no semantic-web-legacy) closed axiom grammar + four-strata store + deterministic engine that (i) answers ONLY what an endorsed axiom licenses (uniqueness never assumed from data, counts never inferred from record enumeration, instance-false only via disjointness — 'a gloss file cannot count parents', operationalised and passing), (ii) refuses everything else with a NAMED code through a pre-registered fail-closed validation order, and (iii) carries provenance + license on every answer. The strict-code refusal leg is where the substance lives: answer-all gets the covered leg free, and abstain-all gets refusal-by-count free, but ONLY a correctly-licensed engine gets both, with the exact code, 300/300. The verifier-not-in-the-vector strata separation held (sidecar + world records reference URNs; concept identity untouched), and the X3 cosine ban is honoured trivially (no similarity step exists anywhere in the answer path). For the correctness thesis this banks the checking INSTRUMENT the thesis needs (E9's constraint-violation arm consumes this engine) — it is deliberately NOT evidence that checking helps anything.",
registry/assessments/oracle-coverage.json:75:    "cross_cutting_theme": "HOW FAR DOES THE MEASURED DETERMINISTIC-GROUNDING CASE REACH? Four threads. (1) THE ENGINE SEAT IS REAL, CHEAP, AND PORTABLE — AS AN INSTRUMENT. Law 3's winning topology needs a deterministic engine that owns correctness; the programme now has one that is MEASURED-sound on two verticals with a byte-identical binary, fail-closed off its slice with named codes, provenance-carrying, and ~10^1 us/query on shared CPU. That is the strongest, cleanest evidence in the whole registry — and it is evidence about the INSTRUMENT, obtained entirely inside the fortress: both evals were authored against the engines' own stores, so exactness there is a consistency-and-licensing property, never world-accuracy. (2) THE TWO BOUNDARY CROSSINGS THAT WOULD MAKE IT MATTER ARE EXACTLY THE UNMEASURED LEGS. For grounding to help an LLM, natural language must reach the closed grammar (l3a-parse / a5-nl: unrun) and a model must be measurably better off with the engine than with the kernel-as-text null and strong baselines (l3a-cost / a5-llm: unrun or under separate contested-audit ruling; f2's secondaries remain MEASURED-UNAUDITED with a known oracle-leakage caveat; f2b-replicate's separation instrument is the template for doing this honestly). Every prior programme lesson says the NL boundary and the null are where mechanisms die; nothing in this batch tests either. (3) COVERAGE IS THE PERIMETER AND IT IS NARROW AND UN-TRANSFERRED. m0b puts the reachable fraction at ~1/3 of content-word mass on the friendliest corpus at the molecules rung — above the niche gate, real, and also the hard ceiling on every covered-slice claim; ASM-0002 (other corpora) is open with one live warning against assuming transfer, and the compression-census's measured engagement (~0.6% at proposition level, same corpus/instance) shows how much thinner USABLE coverage can be than token-mass coverage. (4) NET EPISTEMIC POSITION OF THE CORRECTNESS THESIS: 'a sound, licensed, fail-closed deterministic checker over kernel-governed records exists, extends across domains, and costs microseconds' is now MEASURED and cross-vendor-confirmed at R0. 'That checker, or the kernel it serves, makes any model more correct on any task at matched budget' is UNMEASURED — zero audited end-task wins over the kernel-as-text null. The measured evidence reaches exactly to the fortress wall: everything inside is solid; everything outside is the open half of the thesis, and the successors that decide it are already pre-registered.",
