registry/assessments/oracle-coverage.json:87:    {"fork": "M0B-COVERAGE-GATE (niche-scope banner consequence)", "resolution": "RESOLVED — gate cleared (0.3542 > 0.20): the NICHE-SCOPE banner does not bind on verdict templates and the frontier-pitch coverage-growth cost line is not FORCED (coverage growth remains a live axis on the merits). Corpus/instance-scoped; re-evaluated as the kernel grows (coverage-growth curve RT-11).", "basis": "verdict registry/verdicts/m0b.json, fired_rule_index 2"},
